tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_access_history (
    user_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    login_status TEXT,
    ip_address INET,
    location TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE user_table (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    password VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    last_login TIMESTAMP
);
